Save the following text inti a file called "Genesis1.3.txt"
        
And God said, "Let there be light", and there was light. 
And God saw that the light was good,
 
Run the following program to read the file :

        Dim filename = "Genesis1.3.txt"
        Dim str As String
        str = IO.File.ReadAllText(filename)   

Look at the file in a text editor.
Then look at it in a hex editor.

Delete the file, 
then run the following program to re-write it :
        
        Dim filename = "Genesis1.3.txt"
        IO.File.WriteAllText(filename, "And God said, ""Let there be light"", and there was light." & vbCrLf & "And God saw that the light was good,")
        
 